      • resolve

        public Source resolve(URI uri)
        Resolves URI to RDF/XML. Ignored extensions are rejected. Cached copy is returned, if it exists. Further processing tries to decode a SPARQL query from the query string, and executes it on the endpoint. If there is no query, attempting to load RDF model from URI. Finally the model is serialized as RDF/XML.
        Parameters:
        uri - document URI
        Returns:
        XML source
